{"title":"城市之夜","authors":["董景黎"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":1,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市之夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上海国棉二十九厂  董景黎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月攀上楼顶宽阔的肩膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我泄下水淋淋的乳光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把楼影描摹在平台上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我：这就是城市的夜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——静谧、安详。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，不会的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个窗口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就有一个有趣的故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙，隔开了喧响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别相信这表面的宁静，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"楼的暗角有更暗的身影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灯的光下有更亮的目光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拥挤的城市，距离太近了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切都不能传得很远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任何音都没有回声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许都疲倦了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，正躺在床上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着白花花的屋顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想着已经想过多次的问题，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"其中肯定有一段是关于"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天早上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许都厌烦了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，又在重复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几乎天天说过的那些话。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉拉手，表示亲热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨雪天伞花还会开吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是呵，沉寂的夜真有些闷热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来吧，到星空下来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和我一样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这么站着站着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会有的：田野捎来的风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桃花树上的微笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有海洋……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}